  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200760/extras/3266c1374a4d1e274cf7a613854d9fa0.avif?t=1674165091\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Navigate the small ship and its Crew in a short Adventure. Explore the mysterious, hostile Swamp in North-East Germany filled with secrets and horrors.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200760/extras/8f295fe715bbebb94d64c79c24b934b8.avif?t=1674165091\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Experience the condensed story of the inquisitive Professor and the gruff Captain. The longer they stay in the muddy waters, the greater the impact on their psyche - except if they escape fast enough.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200760/extras/bccd8376bec3b3424b9814b4e0bc63a9.avif?t=1674165091\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>The Story is linear - but it is your decision, how the protagonists process the events and what consequences they draw.<br><br><br>[+] Lovecraftian Horror - but <strong>without jumpscares</strong> nor graphical violence!<br>[+] Navigate the Ship out of a Top-Down perspective. Only Mouse and Keyboard needed.<br>[+] Gather Collectibles to learn more about the unique Lore.<br>[+] Dynamic, but condensed Narrative.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200760/extras/3266c1374a4d1e274cf7a613854d9fa0.avif?t=1674165091\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Navigate the small ship and its Crew in a short Adventure. Explore the mysterious, hostile Swamp in North-East Germany filled with secrets and horrors.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200760/extras/8f295fe715bbebb94d64c79c24b934b8.avif?t=1674165091\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Experience the condensed story of the inquisitive Professor and the gruff Captain. The longer they stay in the muddy waters, the greater the impact on their psyche - except if they escape fast enough.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2200760/extras/bccd8376bec3b3424b9814b4e0bc63a9.avif?t=1674165091\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>The Story is linear - but it is your decision, how the protagonists process the events and what consequences they draw.<br><br><br>[+] Lovecraftian Horror - but <strong>without jumpscares</strong> nor graphical violence!<br>[+] Navigate the Ship out of a Top-Down perspective. Only Mouse and Keyboard needed.<br>[+] Gather Collectibles to learn more about the unique Lore.<br>[+] Dynamic, but condensed Narrative.",
